org.locationtech.geowave.format.stanag4676.parser.model

Class TrackEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.format.stanag4676.parser.model.TrackEvent

  • public class TrackEvent
extends Object
    Provides parameters related to a track.

    Top-level information about the track is expressed in the Track class itself.
